doctype html
html(lang='en')
  head
    title= title
    meta(charset='utf-8')
    meta(name='viewport', content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.min.css')
    script(src='https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.12.4/jquery.min.js')
    script(src='https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.7/js/bootstrap.min.js')
    link(rel='stylesheet', href='/stylesheets/style.css')
  body

block content
  // h1= title
  if activity_list.length!=0
    a(href='activities/export')
      button(type="button", style = 'float: center; background-color: #F24405; border: none; color: white; font-size: 40px; padding: 15px 32px; border-radius: 25px; box-shadow: 0 12px 16px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.24), 0 17px 50px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.19);') Export to Strava
  hr
  a(href='/catalog/user/' + user.id + '/import/')
    button(type="button", style = 'float: left; background-color: #F24405; border: none; color: white; font-size: 20px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 6px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.24), 0 9px 25px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.19);') Import More Activities
  a(href='activities/delete')
    button(type="button", style = 'float: right; background-color: #F24405; border: none; color: white; font-size: 20px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 6px 8px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.24), 0 9px 25px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.19);') Delete All Activities
  br
  br
  br
  p When you export your activities, your Strava account is cross referenced for matching activities. If any activities are listed both on Strava and Running2win, the activity will be updated on Strava with the Running2win comment. If the activity does not exist on Strava, a manual activity will be created using the Running2win activity, including its description. At this time gps files from running2win are not imported. It's something I'm working on. Strava allows you to connect your Garmin account, but it will only import future activities.
  hr
  ul
    each activity in activity_list
      li
        a(href=activity.url) #{activity.name}

    else
      li There are no Activities.
  hr
  p #[strong User: ]
    a(href=user.url) #{user.name}
  if activity_list.length!=0
    p
      a(href='activities/export') Export All Activities to Strava
    p
      a(href='activities/delete') Delete All Activities
